dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Three Sisters quadrangle, San Benito and Santa Clara counties, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Three Sisters, CA 1954. Photorevised 1971. Photoinspected 1978. DMA 1757 IV NE - series V895."
Includes location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1973.
